	("LOC_UNIT_ENKIDU_HD_NAME", 																						 "Enkidu"),
	("LOC_UNIT_ENKIDU_HD_DESCRIPTION", 																			 "Sumerian unique Great Person unit. Combat unit with unique promotion tree. Starts with 1 free promotion.[NEWLINE]+1 [ICON_Strength] Strength per unit killed. +7 [ICON_Strength] Strength when entering new era. Ignores Forest/Jungle [ICON_MOVEMENT] Movement penalties. Military units within 3 tiles gain +100% XP.[NEWLINE]Cannot be built or purchased."),
