	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_LITHUANIAN_UNION_DESCRIPTION",                        "Earn an equal amount of corresponding [ICON_GREATPERSON] Great Person points per turn from an ally for that alliance type. For each Tier building of Holy Site district in Holy City, your [ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Routes to an Ally's city provide +1 [ICON_FAITH] Faith for both cities. Your majority religion becomes the dominant religion in cities that loses a tile to a your Culture Bomb."),
