	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_VICTORIA_ALT_DESCRIPTION",                            "Grant boost [ICON_TECHBOOSTED] to 'Industrialization' each time a Workshop is built (complete 'Industrialization' if already boosted). Cities with Industrial Zone can build one more district than the [ICON_CITIZEN] Population limit allows. Cities with Royal Navy Dockyard provide +2 [ICON_GREATENGINEER] Great Engineer points per turn."),
