	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_HAMMURABI_XP1_DESCRIPTION",                           "[ICON_TECHBOOSTED] Eurekas provide 94% of the [ICON_SCIENCE] Science for technologies. -50% [ICON_SCIENCE] Science per turn."),
