	("LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_LAST_PROPHET_DESCRIPTION",                      "After Political Philosophy is researched, each belief of your Religion provides an additional Cultural policy slot. After founding Religion, provides [ICON_GreatScientist] Great Scientist point, [ICON_GreatWriter] Great Writer point and [ICON_GreatArtist] Great Artist point equal to excess [ICON_GreatPROPHET] Great Prophet points. International [ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Routes spread +200 Religious Pressure of your Religion to the target city."),
	-- 文阿拉伯
	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_RIGHTEOUSNESS_OF_FAITH_DESCRIPTION",                  "City with a Holy Site district can build one more district than the [ICON_CITIZEN] Population limit allows. Each Tier building in Holy Site district provides +5% [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and [ICON_CULTURE] Culture."),
	-- 武阿拉伯
