	("LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_ETHIOPIA_DESCRIPTION",                          "[ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Routes grant +0.5 [ICON_FAITH] Faith per resource at the origin. Improved resources provide +1 [ICON_FAITH] Faith for each copy the city owns. Can purchase Archaeological Museums and Archaeologists with [ICON_FAITH] Faith."),
	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_MENELIK_DESCRIPTION",                                 "Receive [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and [ICON_CULTURE] Culture equal to 15% of your [ICON_FAITH] Faith generation in cities founded on Hills. Units receive +4 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength on Hills."),
