	("LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_GAUL_DESCRIPTION",                              "Mines and Quarry provide a standard adjacency bonus for specialty districts, a Culture Bomb of unowned territory, and receive +1 [ICON_CULTURE] Culture. Unlock the Iron Working technology after properly improving the [ICON_RESOURCE_IRON] Iron."),
