	("LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_MEDITERRANEAN_COLONIES_DESCRIPTION",            "+3 [ICON_HOUSING] Housing and +100% [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production toward settler in coastal cities. Settlers gain +2 [ICON_Movement] Movement and +2 sight range while embarked. Settlers ignore additional [ICON_Movement] Movement costs from embarking and disembarking. Coastal cities adjacent to same sea as their [ICON_Capital] Capital receive +2 [ICON_Citizen] Citizen when established."),
	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_FOUNDER_CARTHAGE_DESCRIPTION",                        "Alliance level reaches Level 3 in one turn. Gain the unique Move Capital project, when first move to a new continent, +50% border expansion rate and send an [ICON_Envoy] Envoy to each City-State on that continent."),
