	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_RAVEN_KING_DESCRIPTION",                              "Levied units gain an ability giving them +2 [ICON_Movement] Movement and +5 [ICON_Strength] Combat Strength. It costs 50% less [ICON_GOLD] Gold and resources to upgrade Levied units. If you Levy troops from a City-State, receive 2 [ICON_ENVOY] Envoys in that City-State. Gain the Black Army unique unit when the Heraldry Civic is researched."),
