	("LOC_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_MONGOLIAN_ORTOO_DESCRIPTION",                   "Starting a [ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Route immediately creates a [ICON_TRADINGPOST] Trading Post in the destination city. Your [ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Routes provide additional +1 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science for passing through each [ICON_TRADINGPOST] Trading Post owned by you. Receive 1 extra level of [ICON_VISLIMITED] Diplomatic Visibility on corresponding Civilization for possessing each [ICON_TRADINGPOST] Trading Post in its Cities. All Mongolian units gain +3 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Bonus from each level of [ICON_VISLIMITED] Diplomatic Visibility."),
	("LOC_TRAIT_LEADER_GENGHIS_KHAN_ABILITY_DESCRIPTION",                    "Pasture tiles provide major adjacency bonus to Commercial Hub districts. All cavalry class units gain +3 [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength and a chance to capture defeated enemy cavalry class units. Combat victories provide [ICON_SCIENCE] Science equal to 50% of the [ICON_STRENGTH] Combat Strength of the defeated unit (on Standard Speed)."),
